Package org.eclipse.rdf4j.query.parser.sparql Description

The rdf4j SPARQL 1.1 parser. This parser produces an algebra model of the query/update string using org.eclipse.rdf4j.queryalgebra.model.
See Also:
SPARQL 1.1 Query, SPARQL 1.1 Update, SPARQL 1.1 Federated Query
